{"tid":1851154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍有癈老疑不滿未能購買口罩　拍打腳踢店舖閘門","createTime":"2020-01-30T02:22:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T02:34:46.000Z","uid":266107,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a11f0358bc659fcb468298f764732f051f8bb3e4","tid":1851154,"uid":266107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T02:22:09.000Z","msg":"【天水圍有市民疑不滿未能購買口罩　拍打腳踢店舖閘門】<br />\n<br />\n一間連鎖店在社交網站指，全線230間分店，今日暫時只能提供每間約20盒口罩，其中在天水圍T Town分店，早上8時已有逾4百人到場排隊，職員其後向排頭20名市民派籌，多名拎不到籌的市民疑不滿安排，多次拍打及踢向店舖閘門，又辱罵店內職員，有人報警求助，多名警員到場了解及維持秩序。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台<br />\n#口罩<br />\n#天水圍<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3177178759056825/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F715486135226112%2Fposts%2F3177178759056825%2F&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rPzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=9555984c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/715486135226112/posts/3177178759056825/</a>"},{"pid":"290e769bded1c274996aab5fadf67159bdc51bcc","tid":1851154,"uid":6557,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T02:24:31.000Z","msg":"D黑警咁斯文"},{"pid":"33b98c66a7b9af9deb475414b201118bc1668363","tid":1851154,"uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T02:24:45.000Z","msg":"屌程班同阿布咪就係呢類人囉"},{"pid":"f78440de18cb168b33fc2ac82150fbce3ed288e0","tid":1851154,"uid":256003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T02:25:57.000Z","msg":"宜家宜個年代有上網訂購，仲嗮9氣排隊。只有d低知識，低文化的廢佬先會做埋咁樣耶。<br />\n<br />\n我深信他們買了幾十盒之後，隔一個月跟住疫情受控，又要扔掉d口罩。白痴。"},{"pid":"3366e7fb3273664cbe9104507c38a73638b7f860","tid":1851154,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T02:26:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a2b42ce9c9cc5b5e154f56e771769dea274847","tid":1851154,"uid":218166,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T02:26:48.000Z","msg":"黑警就開開